text: Zhang Qibin (; born 23 June 1994 in Zibo, Shandong) is a Chinese male swimmer.Zibo Daily: 张麒斌游进里约 (2016-04-10) In the 2016 Olympics, Zhang swam the 100 m butterfly, placing 27th in the final with a time of 52.84 seconds.Zibo Evening Newspaper: 淄博健儿里约创历史 (2016-08-23) ==References== == External links == * * * * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male swimmers Category:Male butterfly swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of China Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Asian Games competitors for China Category:Swimmers at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Sportspeople from Zibo Category:Swimmers from Shandong
title: Zhang Qibin (swimmer)
